node_modules/
dist/
*.db
.env
.claude/settings.local.json
kubectl

.claude/worktrees

# Terraform (state can contain sensitive values; .terraform.lock.hcl IS committed)
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
*.tfplan
# Exception: dev/staging's terraform.tfvars hold non-secret, tracked
# differentiators (cluster_name, capacity types, multi_az, ...) - see
# infra/environments/README.md. Everything else stays covered by *.tfvars
# above, e.g. any local override file with real values.
!infra/environments/*/terraform.tfvars

